00102 template<unsigned DIM>
00103 MooneyRivlinMaterialLaw<DIM>::MooneyRivlinMaterialLaw(double c1, double c2)
00104     : mC1(c1),
00105       mC2(c2)
00106 {
00107     assert(DIM==2 || DIM ==3);
00108 
00109     // If dim==3, check that c2 was passed in, ie c2 isn't the default value
00110     if ((DIM==3) && (c2<MINUS_LARGE+1))
00111     {
00112         EXCEPTION("Two parameters needed for 3d Mooney-Rivlin");
00113     }
00114 
00115     if (c1 < 0.0)
00116     {
00117         EXCEPTION("c1 must be positive in mooney-rivlin"); // is this correct?
00118     }
00119 }
